{"tid":777826,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4平民化身超級英雄 巡街打擊罪惡","createTime":"2018-08-13T08:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T10:02:20.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"549e274dfed52de1d6006a146a414d6530d11deb","tid":777826,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T08:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180812/large/1534058042_5174.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180812%2Flarge%2F1534058042_5174.jpg&h=373272c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180812/large/1534058150_6a06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180812%2Flarge%2F1534058150_6a06.jpg&h=752877ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國利物浦有平民化身真實版「正義聯盟」，4位作超級英雄打扮的正義之士自願在街頭巡邏打擊罪惡。<br />\n<br />\n他們分別是自稱「戰鬥騎士」、現年26歲的店務助理海赫斯特（Roger Hayhurst）；退伍軍人、現職保險經紀的38歲「聖衞士」泰勒（Tim Taylor）；另外還有兩名不願透露姓名的成員：就讀林業的19歲學生「黑武士」，以及現時報稱無業33歲的「激進鬥士」。<br />\n<br />\n他們通常會在晚上出動，配備警用盔甲和越野電單車用的護甲，巡邏罪案頻繁的街道。如果真的遇到罪案發生，就會拍攝下來傳給警方。除此之外，每逢周末他們也會分派食物和飲品予街上的露宿者。目前為止他們直接介入過的案件，是在街上提醒一名男子留意3名女扒手。<br />\n<br />\n4人是受到美國一個叫「啟動」（Initiative）的運動影響展開行動，這個運動主要是鼓勵普通人化身英雄打擊罪案，至今熱潮已經蔓延到英國。<br />\n<br />\n他們強調自己絕對不會濫用私刑，而是希望以和平手段化解罪行。他們說：「我們希望可以勸說人們不要犯罪。說到底，我們這身打扮只是噱頭而己。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180813/58553264\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180813%2F58553264&d=wpE2yiyToc0kp6Chx5CYKZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=4e7d179d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180813%2F58553264&h=9583b862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180813/58553264</a>"},{"pid":"fa23415369dacb62b83b67f10197ef1aea3d429d","tid":777826,"uid":113626,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T08:23:24.000Z","msg":"是但搵個南亞都打得低佢地"},{"pid":"c9e81fd22164ee92d238d5d0ce0b6a0c41e4aac1","tid":777826,"uid":3480,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T08:24:50.000Z","msg":"如果真的遇到罪案發生，就會拍攝下來傳給警方。<br />\n<br />\n搵香港人做咪得<br />\n屙屎唔出都影一餐"},{"pid":"4d020b2906e48e02819ed7da21a00bfd9beb8040","tid":777826,"uid":83609,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T08:24:59.000Z","msg":"如果真的遇到罪案發生，就會拍攝下來傳給警方。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1a3fe15b8c8c3a6e2f87301d96adfa76457f90","tid":777826,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T08:25:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05e0a96eaa34e6ecf8c064feaaa18d509301acc4","tid":777826,"uid":189465,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4d020b2906e48e02819ed7da21a00bfd9beb8040","tid":777826,"uid":83609,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T08:24:59.000Z","msg":"如果真的遇到罪案發生，就會拍攝下來傳給警方。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T08:29:07.000Z","msg":"報警會唔會仲快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0854e97eb46ef4437dff9b539dc41ae640b460ee","tid":777826,"uid":97882,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T08:30:56.000Z","msg":"你班友似賊多啲"},{"pid":"da5939304bff5e85bd502beb9ce299a57fcbd1cb","tid":777826,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:35:37.000Z","msg":"Kick Ass嘅劇情咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77bb8058fcf6ba8d04591fdaf865870b029ffd49","tid":777826,"uid":172297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T09:38:20.000Z","msg":"呢班人想入Marvel定DC？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\